data.description: Welcome Home to the Fabulous Community of Ladera Creek, and Welcome Home to this Beautiful like new 1 Story Lennar Home. Home was built in 2020, and features 3 Bedrooms, Study, Kitchen with Breakfast Area, 36" Cabinets in Kitchen, SS Appliance, New Shelving, Automatic Lighting in the front and back of the home, and so much more. Master Bath Suite features Double Sinks, with Tub and Separate Shower. You will enjoy every moment of this charming and like new home. Mins away from shopping, dining, and entertainment.  Whos Ready to move to Ladera Creek?
